        "title": "-Dspring.profiles.active not recognized under condition",
        "body": "<p>I have passed <code>-Dspring.profiles.active<\/code> as a system property:<\/p>\n\n<pre class=\"lang-xml prettyprint-override\"><code>&lt;bean class=\"org.springframework.beans.factory.config.PropertyPlaceholderConfigurer\"&gt;\n  &lt;property name=\"locations\"&gt;\n    &lt;list&gt;\n      &lt;value&gt;#{'dev' or 'sit' or 'qa'.equals('${spring.profiles.active}')  ? 'classpath:process${spring.profiles.active}.properties' : 'classpath:env/cfg/process-${spring.profiles.active}.properties'}\n      &lt;/value&gt;\n    &lt;/list&gt;\n  &lt;/property&gt;\n&lt;/bean&gt;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>If I pass <strong>dev<\/strong> in <code>spring.profiles.active<\/code> the condition should pass but it is actuallay failing.<\/p>\n\n<p>But it gets updated successfully with <code>Properties<\/code> named <em>process-dev.properties<\/em>.<\/p>\n\n<p>Could someone point out what I am missing?<\/p>\n",
